HEADWORD: Indies
<hw>In"dies</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <def>A name designating
the East Indies, also the West Indies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our king has all the <qex>Indies</qex> in his arms.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

